OL,3,CBeckham thinks Sir Jim Ratcliffe needs
OL,4,Ctime to turn around Manchester United
OL,6,FDavid Beckham is hopeful Sir Jim
OL,7,FRatcliffe will turn Manchester
OL,8,FUnited's fortunes around.
OL,10,FRatcliffe's Ineos took charge of the
OL,11,Fclub's football operations from the
OL,12,FGlazer family in February but United
OL,13,Fhave had an underwhelming start to the
OL,14,Fnew campaign as they look to build on
OL,15,Flast year's FA Cup success.
OL,17,FPressure has mounted on manager Erik
OL,18,Ften Hag, with United sitting 14th in
OL,19,Fthe Premier League after seven games
OL,20,Fand winless in two Europa League
OL,21,Ffixtures.
