OL,3,CBeckham thinks Sir Jim Ratcliffe needs
OL,4,Ctime to turn around Manchester United
OL,6,FBeckham, who won six Premier League
OL,7,Ftitles, two FA Cups and the Champions
OL,8,FLeague during his playing career with
OL,9,FUnited, believes fans will need to be
OL,10,Fpatient with Ratcliffe and his team.
OL,12,F"I think that it definitely needed
OL,13,Fchange," Beckham said on the Rio
OL,14,FFerdinand Presents podcast.
OL,16,F"I think, speaking as a United fan, I
OL,17,Fthink that many people had said that
OL,18,Fthe club needed change and it needed a
OL,19,Ffresh perspective in how this club
OL,20,Fneeds to be run and the decisions that
OL,21,Fare made.
