OL,3,CBeckham thinks Sir Jim Ratcliffe needs
OL,4,Ctime to turn around Manchester United
OL,6,F"I really like Jim. I've met him a few
OL,7,Ftimes over the years with a few mutual
OL,8,Ffriends and I think that he's a fan
OL,9,Fand obviously he's a great businessman
OL,10,Fas well, one of the best and one of
OL,11,Fthe biggest.
OL,13,F"But I think more importantly the fans
OL,14,Fsee that he cares, and I think that's
OL,15,Fa big part of it. I think obviously
OL,16,Fthe fans had lost faith with the
OL,17,Fleadership over the years and
OL,18,Fobviously he really cares about what
OL,19,Fhe wants to do and what he wants to
OL,20,Fcreate.
