OL,3,CBeckham thinks Sir Jim Ratcliffe needs
OL,4,Ctime to turn around Manchester United
OL,6,FInter Miami, who signed Lionel Messi
OL,7,Flast year, have won this season's MLS
OL,8,FSupporters' Shield ` awarded to the
OL,9,Fteam with the best regular season
OL,10,Frecord ` and will be targeting their
OL,11,Ffirst championship when the play-offs
OL,12,Fstart later this month.
OL,14,FThe former England captain said he
OL,15,Flooked to his old Manchester United
OL,16,Fmanager Sir Alex Ferguson for guidance
OL,17,Fwhen founding the club.
OL,19,F"I went to him once and said to him,
OL,20,F'I'm starting this team, how would you
OL,21,Frun it?'," he added.
