OL,3,CBeckham thinks Sir Jim Ratcliffe needs
OL,4,Ctime to turn around Manchester United
OL,6,F"And he sat me down for a couple of
OL,7,Fhours and he told me what I should do
OL,8,Fand what players I should be looking
OL,9,Ffor and how I should run the academy.
OL,11,F"And that's really what I've tried to
OL,12,Fdo. And then I also learnt from people
OL,13,Flike (Real Madrid president)
OL,14,FFlorentino Perez. You know, with
OL,15,FFlorentino, he has this crazy vision
OL,16,Fof always bringing the greatest
OL,17,Fplayers to the club and building this
OL,18,Funbelievable stadium."
